                <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">George Boole: The Father of the Digital Age</h1>
                <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600">How a 19th-Century Mathematician Paved the Way for AI</p>
                <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b3/George_Boole_portrait_c1860s.jpg" alt="Portrait of George Boole" class="slide-image">
                <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                    George Boole's work, created long before computers, is the fundamental logic that makes them work.
                </p>
